Revision history for Perl extension Bio::ViennaNGS::SpliceJunc.

0.01  Mon Sep 15 13:11:17 2014
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.23 with options
		-XA -n ViennaNGS::SpliceJunc
	- added bed6_ss_from_bed12()
	- added bed6_ss_from_segemehl_splits()
	- added novel_sj_from_intersect_annot_segesplit()

0.02  Wed Oct 1 2014
	- updated documentation
	- updated function names
	- added '-nobuf' option to intersectBed syscall
        - added a filter option  for maximum intron length
	- added a filter option for canonical splice junctions
	- use Carp for error handling
	- use Path::Class for path construction
	- use IPC::Cmd for calling third party utilities
	- added tests

0.03  Thu Oct 2 2014
	- changed namespace to Bio::ViennaNGS::SpliceJunc
	- updated documentation

0.04  Fri Oct 3 2014
	- bugfix in MANIFEST 

0.05  Thu Nov 27 2014
	- use Bio::ViennaNGS::Fasta objects
	- added bed6_ss_to_bed12()
	- updated documentation
